<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Vendor Request has been {{decision}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
            color: #2d3748;
            padding: 30px 10px;
        }

        .wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a56a0 0%, #0e3a72 100%);
            padding: 32px 36px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        .status-banner {
            padding: 20px 36px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 22px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .badge-approved {
            background-color: #d1fae5;
            color: #065f46;
        }

        .badge-rejected {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            color: #991b1b;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 8px 36px 28px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #4a5568;
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .info-card {
            background: #f7fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-left: 4px solid #1a56a0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 7px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #edf2f7;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .info-label {
            color: #718096;
            font-weight: 600;
            min-width: 130px;
        }

        .info-value {
            color: #2d3748;
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .notes-box {
            background: #fffbeb;
            border: 1px solid #fcd34d;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            margin: 18px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #92400e;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .notes-box strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .note {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #718096;
            margin-top: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f7fafc;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 18px 36px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #a0aec0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🏦 Vendor Request Update</h1>
            <p>KardexCare Finance Portal</p>
        </div>

        <div class="status-banner">
            {{#if isApproved}}
            <span class="badge badge-approved">✅ Approved</span>
            {{else}}
            <span class="badge badge-rejected">❌ Rejected</span>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hello <strong>{{requesterName}}</strong>,</p>
            <p style="font-size:14px;color:#4a5568;line-height:1.7;">
                Your vendor bank account <strong>{{requestType}}</strong> request has been
                <strong>{{decision}}</strong> by the Finance Admin.
            </p>

            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Request Type</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{requestType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Vendor Name</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{vendorName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Decision</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{decision}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Decided At</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{decidedAt}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if reviewNotes}}
            <div class="notes-box">
                <strong>💬 Review Notes from Admin:</strong>
                {{reviewNotes}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <p class="note">
                {{#if isApproved}}
                The vendor record has been created / updated in the system. You may now proceed with payment processing.
                {{else}}
                Please review the admin notes above and re-submit a corrected request if needed. Contact your Finance
                Admin for further clarification.
                {{/if}}
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message – please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
            <p>© {{currentYear}} KardexCare. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>